        "description": "REST API for game store with JWT auth.\nCRUD for Authors, Games, Customers.\n\n## Auth\nPOST /api/v1/auth/login or /api/v1/auth/register\nHeader: `Authorization: Bearer \u003ctoken\u003e`\n\n## Cascade\n- Author → game_author (games stay)\n- Game → game_author + order_line\n- Customer → cust_order + order_line + order_history + customer_address",
